videos.headline: Boston grabs the and-1 bucket
videos.description: Aliyah Boston gets the and-1 bucket as South Carolina leads vs. Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Boston grabs the and-1 bucket) 2022/3/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cooke knocks down Gamecocks 3-pointer
videos.description: Zia Cooke knocks down the 3-pointer as South Carolina leads Kentucky.

videos.headline: Boston grabs bucket down low
videos.description: Aliyah Boston uses her physicality inside to grab the bucket for the Gamecocks.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Boston grabs bucket down low) 2022/3/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Massengill gets the and-1 bucket for Wildcats
videos.description: Jazmine Massengill makes a great effort to score the and-1 bucket as Kentucky trails vs. South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Massengill gets the and-1 bucket for Wildcats) 2022/3/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kentucky goes wild after stunning South Carolina with late 3
videos.description: Dre'una Edwards hits the go-ahead 3-pointer with 5 seconds remaining as Kentucky defeats South Carolina 64-62 to win the SEC championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kentucky goes wild after stunning South Carolina with late 3) 2022/3/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Elzy on Cats' title: 'We didn't have any quit in us'
videos.description: Following Kentucky's stunning fourth-quarter comeback to secure the SEC Tournament championship, Kyra Elzy salutes her players and coaches.

videos.headline: Edwards' shot seals upset and SEC title for Kentucky
videos.description: Dre'una Edwards caps her 27-point effort with a game-winning 3-pointer to complete 7-seed Kentucky's remarkable comeback over 1-seed South Carolina, 64-62.
